headline: Regions Wealth Management Receives Two Top Industry Awards
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., June 11, 2025--Regions Bank on Wednesday announced its Wealth Management division has received two top industry honors from Global Private Banker’s 2025 Global Private Banking Innovation Awards.
